document_data.caption: A map showing Telchar Lane and surroundings in the Sea Ward of Waterdeep.
document_data.name: Telchar Lane
document_data.mainbody: '''Telchar Lane''' was a small road that was located in the city of [[Waterdeep]].{{Cite interactive atlas|Waterdeep}}
document_data.Location: Telchar Lane was located in the northwestern section of Waterdeep's [[Waterdeep/Sea Ward|Sea Ward]]. The road cut diagonally in between the [[Street of Glances]] and the [[Street of the Singing Dolphin]].
